releaseNotes:
[Important Notice: After pressing the upgrade in the app, single press the device button once to speed up firmware upgrade]
1. In Door and Window mode, a new remote calibration feature is added. In addition to triple pressing the device button for calibration, you can also remotely calibrate the device to closed state via the app. (Hub version ≥ v4.5.50);
2. For Zigbee protocol, vibration detection is added under "Opening and Closing mode" (Hub version ≥ v4.5.60). It can be synchronized to a third-party platform as both a Door and Window Sensor (reporting opening and closing status) and a Presence Sensor (reporting vibration status) simultaneously;
3. For Zigbee protocol, device logic synchronization in "Item Guardian" mode to third-party platforms has been optimized. Now it syncs as one Presence Sensor (reporting vibration status) instead of the original five Wireless Mini Switches (Hub version ≥ v4.5.60);
Note: After upgrading the device firmware, ensure that the Hub is also updated to the latest firmware version to support the new features
